><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71d069108071ffde7604f4c734864f63e7aaefc","tid":1286404,"uid":196077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:12:11.000Z","msg":"城大人成大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc4ed232d740da316f3bdd9ff0a21bc0cb49bcb","tid":1286404,"uid":81309,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"少少 fact check <br />\n文中所講教資會既《大學問責協議》係呢到有得睇：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ugc.edu.hk/big5/ugc/activity/university_acc_agree.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ugc.edu.hk%2Fbig5%2Fugc%2Factivity%2Funiversity_acc_agree.html&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=28551ace\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ugc.edu.hk/big5/ugc/activity/university_acc_agree.html</a><br />\n而參考既教育局問卷既解說：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRCuanV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRCuanV.png&h=6af951ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做左少少圖表方便大家比較<br />\n首先係教育局2016年份報告有幾多僱主請左幾多八大first degree既學生<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jpMF1rW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjpMF1rW.png&h=5a8b08c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以見到「只有X名僱主有聘用X大學生」既講法唔係咁公道<br />\n每間大學畢業生個base都唔一樣 <br />\n無理由話「只有61個僱主有聘用LingU畢業生」咁仆街<br />\n<br />\n跟住係每間大學既平均得分<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98CRoDK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98CRoDK.png&h=c093ebd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住係每間大學係各項評分既比較<br />\n為左方便大家閱讀 我將三大label左做星星<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZSems2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZSems2.png&h=606884b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa44a5c417eeb1982b8919b8f5588f161a69258","tid":1286404,"uid":5866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:14:20.000Z","msg":"喺度偷換概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma